title: Grateful Dead Live at Cumberland County Civic Center on 1986-03-28
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi CR-7A) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.8 MHz) > KORG AudioGate 4 > FLAC; Edited & Mastered in Audacity by Joe Noel: Flac 24/96; Checksum & tags created in xACT
description:
Set 1

Iko Iko-> Beat It On Down The Line, Loser, Good Time Blues, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, Althea, Box Of Rain

Set 2

Playin' In The Band-> Franklin's Tower-> I Need A Miracle-> Playin' In The Band-> Drums-> The Wheel-> Dear Mr. Fantasy-> Playin' In The Band-> Around & Around-> Good Lovin', E: It's All Over Now Baby Blue
